  "title": "Accounts Executive (3 months contract) - WCDT",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Support financial, operational, and compliance audits of the company</p></li><li><p>Assist in scanning, extracting, or downloading documents and data for audit review</p></li><li><p>Follow up with auditees on audit-related emails and communications</p></li><li><p>Help route internal audit reports for approval and signing</p></li><li><p>Maintain and organize hardcopy audit documents</p></li><li><p>Assist with audit tasks using Excel or PowerPoint, and merge PDF documents as needed</p></li><li><p>Undertake ad-hoc duties or projects as assigned<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>**5days work week (Mon-Fri, 8.30am-6.15pm)<br /></p><p><br />Wecruit Pte Ltd | 20C0270<br />Tew Jie Wei | R22106822</p></li></ul>",
